description:
The legendary monster Godzilla is coming to Dave the Diver! 
Battle the giant monster on a submarine!
Collect the monster figures scattered throughout the Blue Hole!

DAVE THE DIVER - Godzilla Content Pack is a time-limited free DLC, only available from [May 23, 07:00 UTC, 2024], until [November 23, 07:59 UTC, 2024]
name: DAVE THE DIVER - Godzilla Content Pack
